Information
------------------------------

Can Property Pay Your Wages?
With UK property prices now at their highest in years, more people are dreaming of carving a living from bricks and mortar. However, without expert advice, mistakes in property development can prove painfully expensive. In this one-off programme, multimillionaire businessman Dave Fishwick lends a hand on projects and finances that are heading for disaster. Dee Lazzerini and her partner Steve Woodford have taken out a mortgage to work on a house in their home patch of Poole, while in Winchester, teacher Elise Farzam and her engineer husband Sam have bought a property that is a potential goldmine - if they can get started on it.
